high_descs: Turn right, then turn left, then turn right to go to the sink.
Remove the spoon from the sink.
Turn around, then turn left, and go to the stove.
Put the spoon in the nearest pot.
Pick up the nearest pot on the stove.
Turn around, then turn left to face the table that is across from the sink.
Place the pot on the table, toward your right.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon in it on the table.

high_descs: walk forwards to the kitchen island, then turn right, and walk over to the kitchen sink near the fridge
grab a spoon out of the sink
turn right and walk over to the kitchen stove ahead
place the spoon inside of the pan on the front left burner
grab the pan off of the front left burner
turn around and walk to the kitchen island and turn left to face it
place the pan down on the kitchen island countertop
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a spoon on it on the kitchen island counter

high_descs: Turn and go to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon that is in the sink to the left of the vase.
Turn to your right and with the spoon go to the stove.
Put the spoon in the pan that is on the left front burner on the stove.
Pick up the pan that is on the left front burner that has the spoon in it.
With the pan that has the spoon in it turn all the way around and go to the table.
Put the pan with the spoon in it on the table on the right front corner.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with spoon on the table
